<div class="com-share" data-id="6012" data-title="《别以为它缺钱，《天将雄师》众筹就是为了收“粉丝”》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/6012/medium/6012.jpg?1436692237" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/6012.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
